A simple Simon Says game made with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
The game shows a sequence of colors, and the player needs to repeat the same sequence.
Each round, the sequence gets longer, making it more challenging.

🎯 How to Play :-
    -> Press the any button to begin the game.
    -> Watch the color sequence shown on the screen.
    -> Click the colors in the same order.
    -> If you get it right, the game adds another color to the sequence.
    -> If you make a mistake, the game ends and you can restart.

🛠️ Tech Used :-
    -> HTML – Game structure
    -> CSS – Styling and layout
    -> JavaScript – Game logic and interactions
